package.name: pantheon-systems/example-drupal8-circle-composer
package.description: Template for creating a project to manage a Drupal site with Composer, and test with Circle CI.  Use `composer create-project` to make your own project, or, if you prefer to clone the git repository, run `composer install` followed by `bin/init-new-project` to replace this file and set up your starting project.
